Nelder-Mead MLE solver for the Weibull series model with masked component cause of failure with observation of exact system lifetime and right censoring.

Source: R/md_mle_wei_series_c1_c2_c3.R
mle_nelder_wei_series_md_c1_c2_c3.Rd

Nelder-Mead MLE solver for the Weibull series model with masked component cause of failure with observation of exact system lifetime and right censoring.

mle_nelder_wei_series_md_c1_c2_c3(
  df,
  theta0,
  hessian = TRUE,
  ...,
  control = list()
)

Arguments

df

data frame, right-censored lifetimes with masked component cause of failure

theta0

initial parameter vector

hessian

logical, if TRUE, then the Hessian is estimated and returned

...

additional arguments passed to loglik_wei_series_md_c1_c2_c3.

control

list of control parameters passed to optim for `Nelder-Mead'

Value

list with components:

  • par final parameter vector

  • value final log-likelihood

  • counts number of function evaluations, gradient evaluations, and Hessian evaluations

  • convergence convergence code

  • message convergence message

  • hessian estimated Hessian
